    "body": "I use cython just to accelerate my code(all written in pure python), so I don't want them to be built when installing them to my developing environment (with `pip install -e`) since it will be inconvenient to debug.  Also the `cythonization` process inside setup.py should not be run. (Compiled version in my situation is tested with CI, so there is no concerns about that.)\r\n\r\nHow should I specify options for not compiling to C and not building? \r\n",
